//- Trigal Media
include ../../mixins/employment-date
div
	div(class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-blue-50/30 to-indigo-50/20 rounded-xl shadow-lg ring-1 ring-[var(--base-color)]/10 p-6 lg:p-8 border-l-4 border-[var(--base-color)] hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300 group backdrop-blur-sm")
		div(class="flex flex-col m:flex-row m:items-start m:justify-between mb-4 gap-3")
			div(class="flex-1")
				h3(class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[var(--base-color)] transition-colors") Trigal Media
				div(class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mb-2")
					span(class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-[var(--base-color)]/10 border border-[var(--base-color)]/15 text-[var(--base-color)] font-semibold") AI-Assisted Product Development
					span(class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-[var(--base-color)]/10 border border-[var(--base-color)]/15 text-[var(--base-color)] font-semibold") RAG Integrations
				h4(class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--base-color)] mb-3") Senior Web Developer Lead
			div(class="flex-shrink-0")
				+employmentDate('Sep 2025 - Current', '9 mos')
		div(class="space-y-4")
			div
				p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--base-color)] uppercase tracking-wide mb-2") Role Overview
				p(class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-base")
					| Part-time frontend technical lead at a Costa Rica–based startup delivering AI-powered applications and MVPs for legal, healthcare, education, and SMB clients. Own frontend architecture, AI-assisted development workflows, code reviews, and mentoring for a small team of primarily junior developers. Make engineering decisions across React, Next.js, Astro, TypeScript, WordPress, Laravel, and RAG-based AI integrations — balancing fast MVP delivery with maintainable, production-ready frontend foundations.
			div(class="space-y-3")
				p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--base-color)] uppercase tracking-wide mb-2") Key Achievements
				ul(class="space-y-2.5 list-none text-gray-700 text-base")
					li(class="flex items-start gap-2")
						span(class="text-[var(--base-color)] font-bold shrink-0") •
						span(class="font-semibold text-gray-900 leading-snug") Lead frontend architecture for AI-assisted MVPs across legal, healthcare, education, and SMB product initiatives
					li(class="flex items-start gap-2")
						span(class="text-[var(--base-color)] font-bold shrink-0") •
						span(class="font-semibold text-gray-900 leading-snug") Integrate AI APIs and RAG workflows into user-facing applications with maintainable, production-ready frontend patterns
					li(class="flex items-start gap-2")
						span(class="text-[var(--base-color)] font-bold shrink-0") •
						span(class="font-semibold text-gray-900 leading-snug") Apply AI-assisted development workflows (Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT) to accelerate debugging, prototyping, and documentation while preserving code review quality
					li(class="flex items-start gap-2")
						span(class="text-[var(--base-color)] font-bold") •
						span Mentor junior developers through code reviews, pairing, and practical frontend standards that improve code quality and delivery consistency
					li(class="flex items-start gap-2")
						span(class="text-[var(--base-color)] font-bold") •
						span Build and refine user-facing features hands-on with React, Next.js, Astro, and TypeScript in fast-moving MVP delivery cycles
					li(class="flex items-start gap-2")
						span(class="text-[var(--base-color)] font-bold") •
						span Define reusable frontend patterns and technical approaches that reduce repetitive setup work across new MVP projects
					li(class="flex items-start gap-2")
						span(class="text-[var(--base-color)] font-bold") •
						span Collaborate with product and design stakeholders to translate requirements into clear frontend execution plans and delivery priorities
			p(class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-5 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100")
				span(class="font-semibold text-[var(--base-color)]") Stack:
				|  React · Next.js · Astro · TypeScript · WordPress · Laravel · AI APIs · RAG · AI-Assisted Development
